<h1>刮</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">guā</span><span class=alesi>(gua1)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 刮 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 刮</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/shave" style="color:black;">shave</a>, <a href="/dictionary/pare" style="color:black;">pare</a> <a href="/dictionary/off" style="color:black;">off</a>, scrape</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 8<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 8 strokes: <a href="/character/的" title="de: possessive, adjectival suffix">的</a>, <a href="/character/和" title="he2: harmony, peace; peaceful, calm">和</a>, <a href="/character/国" title="guo2: nation, country, nation-state">国</a>, <a href="/character/到" title="dao4: go to, arrive, been to">到</a>, <a href="/character/所" title="suo3: place, location; numerary adjunct">所</a>, <a href="/character/事" title="shi4: affair, matter, business; to serve; accident, incident">事</a>, <a href="/character/经" title="jing1: classic works; pass through">经</a>, <a href="/character/法" title="fa3: law, rule, regulation, statute; France, French">法</a>, <a href="/character/学" title="xue2: learning, knowledge; school">学</a>, <a href="/character/现" title="xian4: appear, manifest, become visible">现</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/刀" title="Kangxi radical 18">刀</a>&nbsp;18.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 3 <br><small>Other HSK 3 characters: <a href="/character/姨" title="">姨</a>, <a href="/character/糕" title="gao1: cakes, pastry">糕</a>, <a href="/character/裙" title="qun2: skirt, apron, petticoat">裙</a>, <a href="/character/伞" title="san3: umbrella, parasol, parachute">伞</a>, <a href="/character/衬" title="chen4: underwear; inner garments">衬</a>, <a href="/character/锻" title="duan4: forge metal; temper, refine">锻</a>, <a href="/character/衫" title="shan1: shirt; robe; gown; jacket">衫</a>, <a href="/character/裤" title="ku4: trousers, pants">裤</a>, <a href="/character/矮" title="ai3: short, dwarf; low">矮</a>, <a href="/character/甜" title="tian2: sweet, sweetness">甜</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-3" title="List of HSK 3 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 3 charaters &raquo